RACE.RACE_TEXT: GULFSTREAM PARK RACE 12 5 1/2F All Weather Track CR: 66. Maiden Claiming Purse 21000. FOR MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 125 lbs. Claiming Price $12,500 If no three-year-olds are entered, older weight will revert to 122lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: OMO TEN GIRL set the pace in the two path and drew off under a drive. ALWAYS CONNECTED settled off the early pace while racing three wide, could not match strides with the winner but ran on to gain the place late. VELOCISSIMA raced off the pace three wide and rallied mildly to gain the show. OUTFORARUN bumped with HEADING WEST at the start, pressed the winner in the three path and weakened in the final furlong. HEADING WEST was bumped at the start, raced two wide and never threatened. LOVE UNLIMITED raced off the pace four wide, steadied nearing the eighth pole and improved position. STEPSTONES chased the pace five wide, lugged in nearing the eighth pole and faded. BEER BALI tracked the pace four wide and came up empty in the lane. SPONGER had early speed inside, steadied nearing the turn and faded inside. POMONA'S BULLET was outrun while racing two wide. HEART OF THE BEAST hesitated then hit the gate at the start and trailed throughout.
